title: Be bold. Improve you. Let Hedge be the start of the new you. Apply now
posting_body: ['Our community blends together comfort and a convenient location.', 'We are situated near the many shopping, dining, and entertainment options the area has to offer, including Highland Mall, The Domain, H-E-B, Whole Foods Market, Target, La Marea Restaurant & Seafood, and Buffalo Wild Wings.', 'The Hedge is located in north central Austin and near many area schools and employers, such as Graham Elementary School, Dobie Middle School, Northeast Early College High School, The University of Texas at Austin, Austin Community College, Facebook, Amazon, HomeAway, and Indeed - Austin Domain Tower Office.', "With Highway 183 and Interstate 35 nearby, you'll enjoy convenient access to anywhere in the area.", "Come check out Austin's newest place to call home!", 'Walk ins welcomed!', '-New Vinyl Hardwood Flooring', '-24 hour maintenance', '-New granite counter tops', '-Glass mosaic back splash', '-2" Vinyl Wood Blinds', '-New Fixtures', '-Professionally managed building', '-Tiled tub surround', '-New Cabinets', '-Solar Screens', '-New Bathroom Vanity', '-All new lighting and plumbing fixtures.', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>']
